### ============================================================================
### ONBOARDING — /api/v1/onboarding + /api/v1/useronboardings
### ============================================================================

### ─── User Onboarding ───────────────────────────────────────

### Get my onboarding
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Upsert onboarding
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "nationality": "Nigerian",
  "companyCode": "TRAVELSAFE01",
  "complete": false
}

### Advance onboarding stage
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding/stage
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stage": 3
}

### Get onboarding questions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Save questionnaire responses
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding/questionnaire
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "responses": {
    "age": 35,
    "gender": "male",
    "preexisting_conditions": ["none"],
    "medications": [],
    "allergies": ["penicillin"],
    "travel_frequency": "monthly"
  },
  "complete": true
}

### Save onboarding progress
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentStep": 2,
  "completedSteps": [1],
  "formData": {
    "nationality": "Nigerian",
    "userType": "INDIVIDUAL"
  }
}

### Get onboarding progress
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/onboarding/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ─── Onboarding Records (CRUD) ─────────────────────────────

### List onboarding records (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/useronboardings?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get onboarding record by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/useronboardings/{{onboardingRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create onboarding record
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/useronboardings
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "nationality": "Nigerian",
  "companyCode": "TRAVELSAFE01",
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Update onboarding record
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/useronboardings/{{onboardingRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "INDIVIDUAL",
  "nationality": "Ghanaian",
  "userId": {{userId}}
}

### Delete onboarding record
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/useronboardings/{{onboardingRecordId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
